<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你这混蛋...</b></font>

123
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:31,140
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司 不行的啦</b></font>

124
00:07:31,660 --> 00:07:32,330
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>佐原</b></font>

125
00:07:32,590 --> 00:07:35,800
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>店长也是的 又没有确凿证据 不能说那种话</b></font>

126
00:07:36,360 --> 00:07:38,070
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我只是...</b></font>

127
00:07:38,070 --> 00:07:39,000
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>看我不宰了你</b></font>

128
00:07:39,030 --> 00:07:40,530
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司</b></font>

129
00:07:42,070 --> 00:07:43,470
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>住手啦</b></font>

130
00:07:45,170 --> 00:07:46,970
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>放开我 叫你放开我</b></font>

131
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:48,880
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>会放开你的 会放开你的</b></font>

132
00:07:49,540 --> 00:07:52,110
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>现在先忍一忍 好吗 开司</b></font>

133
00:07:52,280 --> 00:07:54,750
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>别开玩笑了 那混蛋我一定要...</b></font>

134
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:57,680
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那个店长也就嘴上毒</b></font>

135
00:07:57,780 --> 00:08:00,020
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>既不敢赌大钱 也不敢打架的</b></font>

136
00:08:02,590 --> 00:08:05,690
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>就是那德行了 如今的成年人</b></font>

137
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,800
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>别开玩笑了</b></font>

138
00:08:12,530 --> 00:08:13,980
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这是战争啊</b></font>

139
00:08:15,370 --> 00:08:18,650
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>心里怀疑还好说 一旦说出口来</b></font>

140
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:21,980
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>从那一瞬间开始 就是战争了吧</b></font>

141
00:08:26,050 --> 00:08:26,700
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>可恶</b></font>

142
00:08:35,830 --> 00:08:37,320
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司</b></font>

143
00:08:38,790 --> 00:08:44,060
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>哎哟 听我说啊 那个傻瓜店长连我都怀疑了</b></font>

144
00:08:44,100 --> 00:08:47,230
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>还死气白赖的搜了我的身 真是受不了</b></font>

145
00:08:47,630 --> 00:08:50,470
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>因为实在太生气了 我把工作辞了</b></font>

146
00:08:50,970 --> 00:08:51,640
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>辞了?</b></font>

147
00:08:51,970 --> 00:08:57,040
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>嗯 一定是那个傻瓜店长自己丢在什么地方然后忘了</b></font>

148
00:08:58,150 --> 00:09:00,410
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>是吗 你辞了工作啊</b></font>

149
00:09:01,110 --> 00:09:04,250
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这么说...犯人是你吗</b></font>

150
00:09:05,790 --> 00:09:08,960
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>店长很确定他的钱不见了</b></font>

151
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:11,660
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不然的话不会把事情闹那么大</b></font>

152
00:09:12,130 --> 00:09:13,860
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>而事务所只有工作人员才能进来</b></font>

153
00:09:14,800 --> 00:09:19,000
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>偷钱的只可能是我和你 或者那个叫西尾的女孩子</b></font>

154
00:09:19,630 --> 00:09:24,130
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但是西尾一直都在收银台 并没有一个人单独行动的机会</b></font>

155
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,370
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那样的话...</b></font>

156
00:09:25,910 --> 00:09:29,180
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司 别开玩笑了嘛</b></font>

157
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:32,140
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>既然搜身时什么都没找到的话</b></font>

158
00:09:32,550 --> 00:09:35,680
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>就是说你偷了钱之后把它藏在了店里的什么地方</b></font>

159
00:09:36,380 --> 00:09:39,850
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>而为了防止事后有麻烦就把工作也辞了</b></font>

160
00:09:40,620 --> 00:09:42,260
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>难道不是这样吗</b></font>

161
00:09:43,920 --> 00:09:44,820
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司</b></font>

162
00:09:51,780 --> 00:09:53,530
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>真是败了啊</b></font>

163
00:09:57,570 --> 00:09:58,510
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>没辙了</b></font>

164
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:04,440
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>既然你都看穿了我就不客气了</b></font>

165
00:10:06,910 --> 00:10:10,180
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>真是的...当时我真是不知所措了</b></font>

166
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:16,590
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司你突然说如果从包里搜出钱就付100万的时候</b></font>

167
00:10:17,090 --> 00:10:18,760
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你这混蛋</b></font>

168
00:10:19,760 --> 00:10:24,500
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>反正这笔钱也是他从我们打工的钱里剥削出来的脏钱</b></font>

169
00:10:26,830 --> 00:10:28,270
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>今天我请你吃一顿吧</b></font>

170
00:10:29,370 --> 00:10:30,740
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你这家伙...</b></font>

171
00:10:40,590 --> 00:10:42,520
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>居然利用我来运钱</b></font>

172
00:10:43,190 --> 00:10:46,590
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>真是的 差不多该原谅我了嘛</b></font>

173
00:10:46,760 --> 00:10:48,680
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我不是道歉了吗</b></font>

174
00:10:59,610 --> 00:11:05,210
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司你...似乎和普通人有些不一样呢</b></font>

175
00:11:07,110 --> 00:11:10,780
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>该说是危险呢...或者是赚大钱 散发着这样的气息</b></font>

176
00:11:12,380 --> 00:11:16,220
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>对着我这种穷鬼说什么梦话呢</b></font>

177
00:11:18,660 --> 00:11:23,260
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我所说的赚大钱的气息 是指虽然危险但是很好赚的事情</b></font>

178
00:11:23,860 --> 00:11:28,270
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>虽然违法 但只要成功一次就能赚大钱</b></font>

179
00:11:29,270 --> 00:11:33,410
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司你知道这方面的事情吧 我说错了吗</b></font>

180
00:11:36,380 --> 00:11:38,940
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你啊...我怎么会...</b></font>

181
00:11:39,040 --> 00:11:39,950
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你在被人追捕吧</b></font>

182
00:11:41,310 --> 00:11:44,550
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>一开始进的那间店 还有在这里也是</b></font>

183
00:11:44,750 --> 00:11:48,150
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司你所选的都是能看见入口的位子</b></font>

184
00:11:50,220 --> 00:11:54,760
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>而每次有人进来 你都会向入口瞟一眼</b></font>

185
00:11:55,960 --> 00:11:57,630
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这就是有人在追你的证据</b></font>

186
00:11:59,060 --> 00:12:03,370
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>请告诉我吧 我对那种事情超级感兴趣</b></font>

187
00:12:04,270 --> 00:12:06,940
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>别这样 你想太多了傻瓜</b></font>

188
00:12:07,710 --> 00:12:08,570
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不要乱揣测了</b></font>

189
00:12:16,420 --> 00:12:17,650
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我自己都没察觉到</b></font>

190
00:12:18,550 --> 00:12:21,290
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>是吗...原来我下意识有那种动作</b></font>

191
00:12:22,120 --> 00:12:23,440
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我是在害怕吗</b></font>

192
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:24,620
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>害怕他们</b></font>

193
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:28,890
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>还是说是在等待</b></font>

194
00:12:31,460 --> 00:12:33,070
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>哦 开司 这东西</b></font>

195
00:12:34,670 --> 00:12:37,070
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>刚才有个穿黑衣服的男人进来</b></font>

196
00:12:39,640 --> 00:12:42,510
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那个 是手机的号码吧</b></font>

197
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:44,080
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不用打一个吗</b></font>

198
00:12:46,950 --> 00:12:49,820
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>哦 我去上个厕所</b></font>

199
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:07,530
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>是什么人</b></font>

200
00:13:09,990 --> 00:13:12,490
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>报上名来 你找我有事吧</b></font>

201
00:13:14,280 --> 00:13:15,470
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我不是让你报上名...</b></font>

202
00:13:20,550 --> 00:13:21,250
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这声音是...</b></font>

203
00:13:29,710 --> 00:13:31,380
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司啊</b></font>

204
00:13:31,380 --> 00:13:32,090
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>别跟着我</b></font>

205
00:13:33,160 --> 00:13:34,790
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我道歉啦 我道歉啦</b></font>

206
00:13:35,130 --> 00:13:36,970
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我们再去喝吧</b></font>

207
00:13:37,100 --> 00:13:37,760
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>吵死了</b></font>

208
00:13:40,100 --> 00:13:40,730
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司</b></font>

209
00:13:46,200 --> 00:13:46,910
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>远藤</b></font>

210
00:13:48,510 --> 00:13:51,180
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>恭喜你成功生还下来 开司</b></font>

211
00:13:53,580 --> 00:13:54,310
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我送你一程吧</b></font>

212
00:14:01,590 --> 00:14:02,390
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>等一等嘛</b></font>

213
00:14:02,750 --> 00:14:04,090
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>别对我不屑一顾嘛</b></font>

214
00:14:04,860 --> 00:14:08,710
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我给你带来了一个对你而言极好的机会哦</b></font>

215
00:14:09,830 --> 00:14:13,270
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>一个晚上 你的借款就可以清零</b></font>

216
00:14:25,190 --> 00:14:27,850
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>下周六 有个聚会</b></font>

217
00:14:29,880 --> 00:14:32,780
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>现在我正在募集聚会的参加者</b></font>

218
00:14:33,150 --> 00:14:34,780
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>要60人左右</b></font>

219
00:14:35,150 --> 00:14:37,160
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>当然...也是赌博</b></font>

220
00:14:38,160 --> 00:14:40,430
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>只要顺利熬过去一晚就有2000万</b></font>

221
00:14:40,930 --> 00:14:42,560
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不 也许更多...</b></font>

222
00:14:42,560 --> 00:14:43,500
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>适可而止吧</b></font>

223
00:14:43,600 --> 00:14:44,700
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>谁会上你的当</b></font>

224
00:14:44,830 --> 00:14:49,670
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>求您了 请让我参加那个聚会</b></font>

225
00:14:50,140 --> 00:14:51,440
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>傻瓜</b></font>

226
00:14:51,940 --> 00:14:53,870
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我一直都在等待这样的机会</b></font>

227
00:14:54,340 --> 00:14:56,710
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>原来如此 你要试试吗</b></font>

228
00:14:57,780 --> 00:14:59,240
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>傻瓜 住手</b></font>

229
00:14:59,780 --> 00:15:02,210
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那不是你想像中的聚会</b></font>

230
00:15:02,610 --> 00:15:04,020
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>你根本就不知道具体内容</b></font>

231
00:15:04,720 --> 00:15:07,390
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>我明白的 开司你想说的话</b></font>

232
00:15:08,290 --> 00:15:09,620
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>是说很危险吧</b></font>

233
00:15:10,520 --> 00:15:14,360
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>但是啊 我该怎么说呢...</b></font>

234
00:15:14,830 --> 00:15:20,370
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>渐渐明白了 像我们这样的废柴想要发达的话</b></font>

235
00:15:20,800 --> 00:15:22,530
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>就只能在什么地方赚一笔大的</b></font>

236
00:15:23,870 --> 00:15:28,830
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>不然的话是不会有突破口的 无法融入社会</b></font>

237
00:15:30,790 --> 00:15:32,940
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>这是一个突破口啊</b></font>

238
00:15:33,980 --> 00:15:37,050
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>佐原 我不是不理解你的心情</b></font>

239
00:15:37,650 --> 00:15:38,320
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>那样的话...</b></font>

240
00:15:38,550 --> 00:15:39,420
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>即使这样也不行</b></font>

241
00:15:40,690 --> 00:15:44,420
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>清醒一点 不要相信这种可疑的男人的话</b></font>

242
00:15:44,690 --> 00:15:46,120
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>被他的花言巧语所诓骗</b></font>

243
00:15:47,030 --> 00:15:47,690
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>开司</b></font>

244
00:15:47,830 --> 00:15:48,860
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>听我的 再等等吧</b></font>

245
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:52,360
<font face="Zhunyuan" size="21" color="#f0f0f0"><b>适合你的好机会一定会来的</b></font>

